Subject: Missing EPP Client Log Files in Report & Analysis Section
Description:
We wanted to bring to your attention that we have noticed a discrepancy in the log files for our EPP client. Specifically, the logs in the Report and Analysis section are missing, and we only have data from January 2nd, 2025.

Could you please assist us in identifying the possible reason for this issue? The server is running version 5.9.4.0, and the client version is 3.0.3.1.
Solution_Comment__c: The customer confirmed that we can close this ticket after we had a call and we show him how to use the filters and partitions between dates.
